=head1 DESCRIPTION

The configuration that specifies which cookies should be synchronized
from the end user's local browser to the remote browser.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Allowlist => ArrayRef[L<Paws::WorkSpacesWeb::CookieSpecification>]

The list of cookie specifications that are allowed to be synchronized
to the remote browser.


=head2 Blocklist => ArrayRef[L<Paws::WorkSpacesWeb::CookieSpecification>]

The list of cookie specifications that are blocked from being
synchronized to the remote browser.



